msgid "The silhouette of a large clock is reflected here."
msgstr "一座大钟的轮廓在此处倒映出来。"

msgid "A large window shaped like a clock towers above you."
msgstr "一扇形似时钟的大窗户耸立在你的头顶。"

msgid "The time is set to 12:00."
msgstr "时间被设置到了12:00。"

msgid "There you are!"
msgstr "你回来了！"

msgid "How'd you get in there?"
msgstr "你怎么进去的？"

msgid "I got zapped, like there's something keeping me out."
msgstr "我好像被电了一下，像是有什么东西在把我往外推。"

msgid "Really?"
msgstr "真的吗？"

msgid "You didn't even notice me gone!?"
msgstr "你都没发现我不见了吗！？"

msgid "...."
msgstr "...."

msgid "No."
msgstr "没发现。"

msgid "Cold..."
msgstr "好冷淡..."

msgid "So what was in there anyway?"
msgstr "所以，里面有些什么呢？"

msgid "Anything fun?"
msgstr "好不好玩？"

msgid "Yes, very fun."
msgstr "好玩，非常好玩。"

msgid "What? Really??"
msgstr "什么？真的吗？？"

msgid "What was it?"
msgstr "是什么东西啊？"

msgid "I can't tell you."
msgstr "我不能告诉你。"

msgid "Huh?!"
msgstr "啊？！"

msgid "Why not??"
msgstr "为什么不告诉我呢？？"

msgid "Because it's more fun that way."
msgstr "因为这样更好玩。"

msgid "No way, don't do me dirty like this!"
msgstr "别吧，别对我玩这种脏把戏啊！"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "(It's strange though. Why wasn't he able to enter?)"
msgstr "（总之很奇怪。为什么他不能进去呢？）"
